examples.text: Mr. <w>Michie</w> has been a respected lawyer in this town for over thirty years.
The <w>Michie</w> family organizes a large reunion every summer in the park.

senses.sense_definition: A female given name from Japanese.

examples.text: My friend <w>Michie</w> is traveling to Tokyo to visit her relatives.
She chose the name <w>Michie</w> for her daughter to honor her Japanese heritage.

senses.sense_definition: A town in McNairy County, Tennessee, United States.

examples.text: We stopped in <w>Michie</w> to buy gas while driving through Tennessee.
The small town of <w>Michie</w> is known for its quiet and friendly atmosphere.
